---
import HeadingLarge from "@components/HeadingLarge.astro";
import Text from "@components/Text.astro";
import View from "@components/View.astro";
import Group from "@components/Group.astro";
import { Layout } from "@layouts";
import Image from "@components/Image.astro";
import Heading from "@components/Heading.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Starboard | Work | Jonathon Toon | Software Designer & Product Leader"
  description="Jonathon Toon is a versatile software designer and product leader based in Aotearoa New Zealand."
  keywords="design, software, product, fractional, leadership, new zealand, aotearoa, technology, typescript, start ups, engineering, mentorship, coaching, adplist"
  twitterHandle="@jonathontoon"
  canonicalUrl="https://www.jonathontoon.com/"
  ogImage="/images/og-image.png"
>
  <Group>
    <HeadingLarge class="px-2">Starboard</HeadingLarge>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Starboard is a maritime intelligence platform processing 4,000+ vessel
      positions per second for government agencies across New Zealand,
      Australia, and the Pacific.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Following their last raise, I partnered with the Chief of Marketing and
      Product to refresh Starboard's website, to improve content discovery and
      lead generation while transitioning off legacy technologies.
    </Text>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <View class="px-2">
      <View class="h-px w-full bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-700" />
    </View>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Heading class="px-2">Website</Heading>
    <Text class="px-2">
      When visting Starboard's website, agencies evaluating their product
      struggled to find the relevant information that matched their needs.
      Despite the weath of webinars and field operation reports a lot of
      information was burried under generic pages and hidden directories.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Working with Sales and Customer Success teams, I learn't that prospects
      needed to see evidence of successful deployments before diving into
      technical specs.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Decision-makers wanted proof that similar agencies had solved comparable
      challenges.
    </Text>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-one.png"
      alt="Homepage design showcasing maritime surveillance expertise and global reach."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-two.png"
      alt="Solutions page highlighting real-time vessel tracking and analytics capabilities."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Redesigned and built more than 20 new pages on Webflow, including
      migration of 100+ articles, field reports, and webinars from their legacy
      system.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      This meant creating a clear structure with easy navigation, better SEO
      categories, and ways for visitors to find content that matched how they
      actually searched for intelligence solutions.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      I also created a pricing page with separated tiers, information that had
      previously only existed behind closed sales meetings. This transparency
      helped prospects self-qualify and gave them clearer expectations before
      engaging with the sales team.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Along with the website redesign, I created clear maintenance documentation
      for in-house teams, enabling them to manage content updates and basic site
      modifications without external support.
    </Text>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-three.png"
      alt="Resource center design organizing maritime intelligence insights and case studies."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-four.png"
      alt="About page emphasizing team expertise and company mission in ocean protection."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-five.png"
      alt="About page emphasizing team expertise and company mission in ocean protection."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Text class="px-2">
      After the website launch, the reorganized content helped visitors quickly
      find relevant case studies and technical details for their specific needs,
      whether border security, fisheries management, or environmental
      monitoring.
    </Text>
  </Group>
</Layout>
